{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":426,"text":"Good afternoon."},{"time":1747,"text":"I am not a farmer."}]},{"cues":[{"time":4690,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":5625,"text":"I'm not. I'm a parent, I'm a resident and I'm a teacher."},{"time":9177,"text":"And this is my world."},{"time":10739,"text":"And along the way I've started noticing --"},{"time":12352,"text":"I'm on my third generation of kids --"},{"time":13821,"text":"that they're getting bigger."},{"time":15074,"text":"They're getting sicker."},{"time":16233,"text":"In addition to these complexities,"},{"time":18217,"text":"I just learned that 70 percent of the kids that I see"},{"time":20130,"text":"who are labeled learning disabled would not have been"},{"time":22140,"text":"had they had proper prenatal nutrition."}]},{"cues":[{"time":24497,"text":"The realities of my community are simple. They look like this."},{"time":28173,"text":"Kids should not have to grow up and look at things like this."},{"time":30907,"text":"And as jobs continue to leave my community,"},{"time":33049,"text":"and energy continues to come in, be exported in,"},{"time":35992,"text":"it's no wonder that really some people refer to the South Bronx as a desert."},{"time":41327,"text":"But I'm the oldest sixth grader you'll ever meet,"},{"time":43927,"text":"so I get up every day with this tremendous amount of enthusiasm"},{"time":46560,"text":"that I'm hoping to share with you all today."},{"time":48896,"text":"And with that note, I come to you with this belief"},{"time":52373,"text":"that kids should not have to leave their communities"},{"time":54847,"text":"to live, learn and earn in a better one."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56228,"text":"So I'm here to tell you a story about me"},{"time":57866,"text":"and this wall that I met outside, which I'm now bringing inside."},{"time":61387,"text":"And it starts with three people."},{"time":63130,"text":"The crazy teacher -- that's me on the left,"},{"time":65208,"text":"I dress up pretty, thank you, my wife, I love you for getting a good suit --"},{"time":68586,"text":"my passionate borough president"},{"time":70250,"text":"and a guy named George Irwin from Green Living Technologies"},{"time":72795,"text":"who helped me with my class"},{"time":74059,"text":"and helped me get involved with this patented technology."},{"time":76546,"text":"But it all starts with seeds in classrooms,"},{"time":79410,"text":"in my place, which looks like this."},{"time":82066,"text":"And I'm here today hoping that my reach will exceed my grasp."},{"time":87719,"text":"And that's really what this is all about."}]},{"cues":[{"time":89418,"text":"And it starts with incredible kids like this,"},{"time":91154,"text":"who come early and stay late."},{"time":92875,"text":"All of my kids are either IEP or ELL learners,"},{"time":95843,"text":"most come with a lot of handicaps,"},{"time":97602,"text":"most are homeless and many are in foster care."},{"time":100155,"text":"Almost all of my kids live below poverty."},{"time":102406,"text":"But with those seeds, from day one, we are growing in my classroom,"},{"time":105827,"text":"and this is what it looks like in my classroom."},{"time":108018,"text":"And you see how attentive these kids are to these seeds."},{"time":110619,"text":"And then you notice that those seeds become farms across the Bronx that look like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":115058,"text":"But again, I am not a farmer. I'm a teacher."},{"time":119275,"text":"And I don't like weeding, and I don't like back-breaking labor."},{"time":121931,"text":"So I wanted to figure out how I could get this kind of success"},{"time":124059,"text":"into something small, like this,"},{"time":126427,"text":"and bring it into my classroom so that handicapped kids could do it,"},{"time":129219,"text":"kids who didn't want to be outside could do it,"},{"time":130941,"text":"and everyone could have access."},{"time":132241,"text":"So I called George Irwin, and what do you know?"},{"time":134374,"text":"He came to my class and we built an indoor edible wall."},{"time":138035,"text":"And what we do is we partner it with authentic learning experiences,"},{"time":141383,"text":"private-based learning."},{"time":143090,"text":"And lo and behold, we gave birth to"},{"time":145714,"text":"the first edible wall in New York City."}]},{"cues":[{"time":147962,"text":"So if you're hungry, get up and eat."},{"time":149122,"text":"You can do it right now. My kids play cow all the time."},{"time":150946,"text":"Okay? But we were just getting started,"},{"time":154298,"text":"the kids loved the technology,"},{"time":155667,"text":"so we called up George and we said, \"We gotta learn more!\""},{"time":158012,"text":"Now, Mayor Bloomberg, thank you very much, we no longer need work permits,"},{"time":160867,"text":"which comes with slices and bonded contractors -- we're available for you --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":163644,"text":"We decided to go to Boston."},{"time":165650,"text":"And my kids, from the poorest congressional district in America,"},{"time":168076,"text":"became the first to install a green wall,"},{"time":171341,"text":"designed by a computer, with real-live learning tools,"},{"time":173626,"text":"21 stories up -- if you're going to go visit it,"},{"time":175175,"text":"it's on top of the John Hancock building."},{"time":177234,"text":"But closer to home, we started installing these walls in schools"},{"time":180026,"text":"that look like this with lighting like that,"},{"time":181946,"text":"real LED stuff, 21st-century technology."},{"time":185035,"text":"And what do you know? We made 21st century money,"},{"time":187354,"text":"and that was groundbreaking. Wow!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":190173,"text":"This is my harvest, people."},{"time":192985,"text":"And what do you do with this food? You cook it!"},{"time":195742,"text":"And those are my heirloom students making heirloom sauce,"},{"time":198646,"text":"with plastic forks, and we get it into the cafeteria,"},{"time":201108,"text":"and we grow stuff and we feed our teachers."},{"time":203308,"text":"And that is the youngest nationally certified"},{"time":205519,"text":"workforce in America with our Bronx Borough President."}]},{"cues":[{"time":208342,"text":"And what'd we do then? Well, I met nice people like you,"},{"time":211246,"text":"and they invited us to the Hamptons."},{"time":212983,"text":"So I call this \"from South Bronx to Southampton.\""},{"time":215254,"text":"And we started putting in roofs that look like this,"},{"time":217759,"text":"and we came in from destitute neighborhoods"},{"time":220047,"text":"to start building landscape like this, wow! People noticed."},{"time":223615,"text":"And so we got invited back this past summer,"},{"time":225609,"text":"and we actually moved into the Hamptons,"},{"time":227368,"text":"payed 3,500 dollars a week for a house, and we learned how to surf."},{"time":230191,"text":"And when you can do stuff like this --"},{"time":232967,"text":"These are my kids putting in this technology,"},{"time":236183,"text":"and when you can build a roof that looks like that"},{"time":238720,"text":"on a house that looks like that"},{"time":241134,"text":"with sedum that looks like this,"},{"time":243944,"text":"this is the new green graffiti."}]},{"cues":[{"time":246686,"text":"So, you may wonder what does a wall like this"},{"time":250191,"text":"really do for kids, besides changing landscapes and mindsets?"},{"time":252751,"text":"Okay, I'm going to tell you what it does."},{"time":254647,"text":"It gets me to meet incredible contractors like this,"},{"time":256967,"text":"Jim Ellenberger from Ellenberger Services."},{"time":259119,"text":"And this is where it becomes true triple bottom line."},{"time":261852,"text":"Because Jim realized that these kids, my future farmers,"},{"time":265341,"text":"really had the skills he needed to build affordable housing"},{"time":268225,"text":"for New Yorkers, right in their own neighborhood."},{"time":270423,"text":"And this is what my kids are doing, making living wage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":272767,"text":"Now, if you're like me, you live in a building, there are seven guys"},{"time":275607,"text":"out of work looking to manage a million dollars."},{"time":277622,"text":"I don't have it. But if you need a toilet fixed"},{"time":280031,"text":"or, you know, some shelving, I gotta wait six months"},{"time":282042,"text":"for an appointment with someone who drives a much nicer car than me."},{"time":284495,"text":"That's the beauty of this economy."},{"time":286274,"text":"But my kids are now licensed and bonded in trade."},{"time":289608,"text":"And that's my first student to open up, the first in his family to have a bank account."},{"time":292584,"text":"This immigrant student is the first one in his family to use an ATM."},{"time":295993,"text":"And this is the true triple bottom line,"},{"time":298375,"text":"because we can take neighborhoods that were abandoned and destitute"},{"time":300630,"text":"and turn them into something like this with interiors like this."}]},{"cues":[{"time":303551,"text":"Wow! People noticed. And notice they did."},{"time":305630,"text":"So CNN called, and we were delighted to have them come to our farmer's market."},{"time":309126,"text":"And then when Rockefeller Center said, NBC,"},{"time":311694,"text":"could you put this thing up on the walls? We were delighted."},{"time":313598,"text":"But this, I show you, when kids from the poorest congressional district in America"},{"time":317590,"text":"can build a 30-foot by 15-foot wall,"},{"time":320310,"text":"design it, plant it and install it in the heart of New York City,"},{"time":323475,"text":"that's a true \"s√≠ se puede\" moment."},{"time":325494,"text":"Really scholastic, if you ask me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":327879,"text":"But this is not a Getty image."},{"time":330150,"text":"That's a picture I took of my Bronx Borough President,"},{"time":332726,"text":"addressing my kids in his house, not the jailhouse,"},{"time":335941,"text":"making them feel a part of it."},{"time":337488,"text":"That's our State Senator Gustavo Rivera and Bob Bieder,"},{"time":339842,"text":"coming to my classroom to make my kids feel important."},{"time":342442,"text":"And when the Bronx Borough President shows up"},{"time":344160,"text":"and the State Senator comes to our class,"},{"time":346342,"text":"believe you me, the Bronx can change attitudes now."},{"time":350086,"text":"We are poised, ready, willing and able"},{"time":351608,"text":"to export our talent and diversity in ways we've never even imagined."},{"time":354808,"text":"And when the local senator gets on the scale in public"},{"time":356874,"text":"and says he's got to lose weight, so do I!"},{"time":360087,"text":"And I tell you what, I'm doing it and so are the kids."}]},{"cues":[{"time":362952,"text":"Okay? And then celebrities started."},{"time":365030,"text":"Produce Pete can't believe what we grow."},{"time":367046,"text":"Lorna Sass came and donated books."},{"time":369262,"text":"Okay? We're feeding seniors."},{"time":371494,"text":"And when we realized that we were growing for food justice in the South Bronx,"},{"time":375055,"text":"so did the international community."},{"time":376940,"text":"And my kids in the South Bronx were repped in"},{"time":378510,"text":"the first international green roof conference."},{"time":380686,"text":"And that's just great."}]},{"cues":[{"time":382118,"text":"Except what about locally?"},{"time":383729,"text":"Well, we met this woman, Avis Richards, with the Ground Up Campaign."},{"time":386793,"text":"Unbelievable! Through her, my kids,"},{"time":389153,"text":"the most disenfranchised and marginalized,"},{"time":391281,"text":"were able to roll out 100 gardens to New York City public schools."},{"time":395050,"text":"That's triple bottom line! Okay?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":397907,"text":"A year ago today, I was invited to the New York Academy of Medicine."},{"time":400842,"text":"I thought this concept of designing a strong and healthy New York"},{"time":404306,"text":"made sense, especially when the resources were free."},{"time":407017,"text":"So thank you all and I love them."},{"time":408793,"text":"They introduced me to the New York City Strategic Alliance for Health,"},{"time":411811,"text":"again, free resources, don't waste them."},{"time":414775,"text":"And what do you know? Six months later,"},{"time":416921,"text":"my school and my kids were awarded the first ever"},{"time":420020,"text":"high school award of excellence for creating a healthy school environment."},{"time":423707,"text":"The greenest class in New York City."},{"time":425833,"text":"But more importantly is my kids learned to get,"},{"time":428275,"text":"they learned to give."},{"time":429908,"text":"And we took the money that we made from our farmer's market,"},{"time":432377,"text":"and started buying gifts for the homeless"},{"time":433825,"text":"and for needy around the world."},{"time":435265,"text":"So we started giving back."},{"time":436675,"text":"And that's when I realized that the greening of America"},{"time":439174,"text":"starts first with the pockets, then with the heart"},{"time":442409,"text":"and then with the mind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":443627,"text":"So we were onto something, and we're still onto something."},{"time":445958,"text":"And thank God Trinity Wall Street noticed,"},{"time":447792,"text":"because they gave us the birth of Green Bronx Machine."},{"time":451025,"text":"We're 3,000 strong right now."},{"time":452832,"text":"And what does it really do?"},{"time":454153,"text":"It teaches kids to re-vision their communities,"},{"time":456187,"text":"so when they grow up in places like this, they can imagine it like this."},{"time":459233,"text":"And my kids, trained and certified --"},{"time":461376,"text":"Ma, you get the tax abatement. Thank you, Mayor Bloomberg --"},{"time":463368,"text":"can take communities that look like this and convert them into things that look like that,"},{"time":467075,"text":"and that to me, people, is another true \"s√≠ se puede\" moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":470464,"text":"Now, how does it start? It starts in schools."},{"time":472544,"text":"No more little Knicks and little Nets."},{"time":474264,"text":"Group by broccoli, group by your favorite vegetable,"},{"time":477674,"text":"something you can aspire to."},{"time":479305,"text":"Okay? And these are my future farmers of America,"},{"time":481352,"text":"growing up in Brook Park on 141st Street,"},{"time":483825,"text":"the most migrant community in America."},{"time":485552,"text":"When tenacious little ones learn how to garden like this,"},{"time":487640,"text":"it's no wonder we get fruit like that."},{"time":490001,"text":"And I love it! And so do they."},{"time":491992,"text":"And we're building teepees in neighborhoods that were burning down."},{"time":494907,"text":"And that's a true \"s√≠ se puede\" moment."},{"time":497280,"text":"And again, Brook Park feeds hundreds of people"},{"time":500657,"text":"without a food stamp or a fingerprint."},{"time":503075,"text":"The poorest congressional district in America,"},{"time":505128,"text":"the most migratory community in America, we can do this."},{"time":508312,"text":"Bissel Gardens is cranking out food in epic proportions,"},{"time":512016,"text":"moving kids into an economy they never imagined."}]},{"cues":[{"time":514320,"text":"Now, somewhere over the rainbow, my friends,"},{"time":516784,"text":"is the South Bronx of America. And we're doing it."},{"time":520512,"text":"How does it start? Well, look at Jose's attention to detail."},{"time":523367,"text":"Thank God Omar knows that carrots come from the ground,"},{"time":526008,"text":"and not aisle 9 at the supermarket"},{"time":527584,"text":"or through a bullet-proof window or through a piece of styrofoam."},{"time":530375,"text":"And when Henry knows that green is good, so do I."},{"time":533075,"text":"And when you expand their palates, you expand their vocabulary."},{"time":536129,"text":"And most importantly, when you put big kids together with little kids,"},{"time":539762,"text":"you get the big fat white guy out of the middle, which is cool,"},{"time":542109,"text":"and you create this kind of accountability amongst peers, which is incredible."}]},{"cues":[{"time":545541,"text":"God, I'm going to run out of time, so I've gotta keep it moving."},{"time":548130,"text":"But this is my weekly paycheck for kids; that's our green graffiti."},{"time":551330,"text":"This is what we're doing."},{"time":552995,"text":"And behold the glory and bounty that is Bronx County."},{"time":557474,"text":"Nothing thrills me more than to see kids pollinating plants instead of each other."},{"time":560817,"text":"I gotta tell you, I'm a protective parent."},{"time":562977,"text":"But those kids are the kids who are now putting"},{"time":564518,"text":"pumpkin patches on top of trains."},{"time":566394,"text":"We're also designing coin ponds for the rich and affluent."},{"time":569235,"text":"We're also becoming children of the corn,"},{"time":570941,"text":"creating farms in the middle of Fordham Road for awareness"},{"time":573545,"text":"and window bottles out of garbage."}]},{"cues":[{"time":575098,"text":"Now I don't expect every kid to be a farmer,"},{"time":576897,"text":"but I expect you to read about it, write about it, blog about it, offer outstanding customer service."},{"time":580258,"text":"I expect them to be engaged, and man, are they!"},{"time":582745,"text":"So that's my incredible classroom, that's the food."},{"time":585129,"text":"Where does it go? Zero miles to plate, right down into the cafeteria."},{"time":588929,"text":"Or more importantly, to local shelters,"},{"time":591008,"text":"where most of our kids are getting one to two meals a day."},{"time":593361,"text":"And we're stepping it up."},{"time":595049,"text":"No Air Jordans were ever ruined on my farm."},{"time":597611,"text":"And in his day, a million dollar gardens and incredible installations."}]},{"cues":[{"time":600890,"text":"Let me tell you something, people."},{"time":602530,"text":"This is a beautiful moment."},{"time":606436,"text":"Black field, brown field, toxic waste field, battlefield --"},{"time":609621,"text":"we're proving in the Bronx that you can grow anywhere, on cement."},{"time":612476,"text":"And we take orders for flowers. I'm putting the bake sale to shame."},{"time":616397,"text":"We take orders now. I'm booking for the spring."},{"time":618429,"text":"And these were all grown from seeds. We're learning everything."},{"time":621797,"text":"And again, when you can take kids from backgrounds as diverse"},{"time":624693,"text":"as this to do something as special as this,"},{"time":626750,"text":"we're really creating a moment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":628474,"text":"Now, you may ask about these kids."},{"time":631190,"text":"Forty percent attendance to 93 percent attendance."},{"time":634371,"text":"All start overage and under-credit."},{"time":637260,"text":"They are now, my first cohort is all in college, earning a living wage."},{"time":641196,"text":"The rest are scheduled to graduate this June."},{"time":643477,"text":"Happy kids, happy families, happy colleagues."},{"time":646429,"text":"Amazed people. The glory and bounty that is Bronx County."}]},{"cues":[{"time":650565,"text":"Let's talk about mint. Where is my mint?"},{"time":652828,"text":"I grow seven kinds of mint in my class."},{"time":655016,"text":"Mojitos, anybody? I'll be at Telepan later."},{"time":657167,"text":"But, understand this is my intellectual Viagra."},{"time":660362,"text":"Ladies and gentlemen, I gotta move quick, but understand this:"},{"time":663562,"text":"The borough that gave us baggy pants and funky fresh beats"},{"time":666298,"text":"is becoming home to the organic ones."},{"time":668450,"text":"My green [unclear] 25,000 pounds of vegetables,"},{"time":671386,"text":"I'm growing organic citizens, engaged kids."},{"time":674698,"text":"So help us go from this to this."},{"time":677408,"text":"Self-sustaining entities, 18 months return on investment,"},{"time":680698,"text":"plus we're paying people living wage and health benefits,"},{"time":682890,"text":"while feeding people for pennies on the dollar."}]},{"cues":[{"time":684746,"text":"Martin Luther King said that people need to be uplifted with dignity."},{"time":688362,"text":"So here in New York, I urge you, my fellow Americans,"},{"time":691627,"text":"to help us make America great again."},{"time":694274,"text":"It's simple. Share your passion."},{"time":696218,"text":"It's real easy. Go see these two videos, please."},{"time":698643,"text":"One got us invited to the White House, one's a recent incarnation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":701542,"text":"And most importantly, get the biggest bully out of schools."},{"time":704176,"text":"This has got to go tomorrow."},{"time":706281,"text":"People, you can all do that."},{"time":708342,"text":"Keep kids out of stores that look like this."},{"time":711578,"text":"Make them a healthy plate,"},{"time":713275,"text":"especially if you can pick it off the wall in your own classroom -- delicioso!"},{"time":716026,"text":"Model good behavior. Get them to a green cart."},{"time":719362,"text":"Big kids love strawberries and bananas."},{"time":721578,"text":"Teach them entrepreneurship. Thank God for GrowNYC."},{"time":724594,"text":"Let them cook. Great lunch today, let them do culinary things."},{"time":727826,"text":"But most importantly, just love them."},{"time":729745,"text":"Nothing works like unconditional love."}]},{"cues":[{"time":732059,"text":"So, my good friend Kermit said it's not easy being green."},{"time":735266,"text":"It's not. I come from a place where kids can buy"},{"time":737950,"text":"35 flavors of blunt wrap at any day of the moment,"},{"time":740975,"text":"where ice cream freezers are filled with slushy malt liquor."},{"time":743626,"text":"Okay? My dear friend Majora Carter once told me,"},{"time":748013,"text":"we have everything to gain and nothing to lose."},{"time":751276,"text":"So here, and at a time when we've gone from"},{"time":753528,"text":"the audacity to hope to hope for some audacity,"},{"time":756083,"text":"I urge you to do something."},{"time":757978,"text":"I urge you to do something."}]},{"cues":[{"time":759449,"text":"Right now, we're all tadpoles,"},{"time":761193,"text":"but I urge you to become a big frog and take that big, green leap."},{"time":764487,"text":"I don't care if you're on the left, on the right, up the middle, wherever."},{"time":767781,"text":"Join me. Use -- I've got a lot of energy. Help me use it."},{"time":771541,"text":"We can do something here."},{"time":774175,"text":"And along the way, please take time to smell the flowers,"},{"time":776845,"text":"especially if you and your students grew them."}]},{"cues":[{"time":778382,"text":"I'm Steve Ritz, this is Green Bronx Machine."},{"time":780981,"text":"I've got to say thank you to my wife and family, for my kids,"},{"time":784350,"text":"thank you for coming every day, and for my colleagues,"},{"time":786108,"text":"believing and supporting me."},{"time":787542,"text":"We are growing our way into a new economy."},{"time":789675,"text":"Thank you, God bless you and enjoy the day. I'm Steve Ritz."}]},{"cues":[{"time":792876,"text":"S√≠ se puede!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":795042,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}